latestIgtvVideos.caption:
From scraping to polishing, and from painting to adorning, we had been an integral part of giving this deity a look that I have always dreamt of.  However should I be honest about it, that we have been carrying out job to clean, scrape and repaint the deity for almost 6 years, none of the year happened that we must give her a look of a old Bengal deity, must have we flown obedient to the stream of modernity until this year. This year we tried to give a look of an old Bengal deity that dates back to 200 years perhaps as old as the deity, I am certain that there are many flaws, however we simply tried our best. Here is a small video where we tried to compact the entire process . Thank you for watching. 

Thanking you @arnab4668 as u helped me with the description.

A fresh , dewy makeup with the beautiful curls and those pretty floral arrangements for her engagement.

🌸🌸 RECEPTION 🌸🌸

What an extremely kind and sweet Bride we had the pleasure to get ready for her reception. A person with impeccable taste in clothing and ensembles. It lit my heart seeing the gorgeous gorgeous EKAYA saree which wrapped her like it was meant merely very much for her. Along with that the lovely traditional Jewelleries and exquisite, soft, make up and hair just added another dimension to the entire look which brought out her inner innocence and kindness and softness in the appearance. Absolutely loved our beautiful bride SAMADRITA ❤️🧿❤️🌸
